  "plan": "Create a corrected isolated integer encoder using `low`/`range` instead of `fraction`/`range`. Encode value 7 with `get_integer(9,0)` and run it through the already-built `/tmp/dec_int` decoder. If it decodes to 7, the core arithmetic coder is correct and can be extended to literals/LZ. If not, the debug trace will show the next divergence.",
